whole_object: This boardroom is so fancy, it looks like even the chairs are having a meeting of the 'knotty' pine committee.
single_object:
- Table: "I told the table to take a break, but it just couldn't handle the pressure of all those meetings!"
- Chairs: "These chairs are so supportive, they should start a motivational speaking tour!"
- Curtains: "The curtains are great at keeping secrets; they never let the light in on the gossip!"
- Trophy: "This trophy is a real show-off; it always wants to be the center of attention!"
- Painting: "The painting is so well-done, it could probably teach a class on how to hang around!"
- Window: "The window has a clear view on life, but it still can't see why people love to stare!"
- Lamp: "This lamp is always brightening up the room, but it really needs to work on its light-hearted jokes!"
- Cabinet: "The cabinet is a real hoarder; it just can't resist keeping all the best stories behind closed doors!"
- Books: "These books are so full of knowledge, they should start charging for their wisdom!" 
- Model ship: "The model ship is always ready to sail into new adventures, but it never leaves the dock!"
